snippet.title: Rogue Flight - Announcement Trailer | PS5 Games
snippet.description:
Traverse the Sol system in this breathtaking arcade space combat inspired by the landmark style of 80's and 90's prestige anime and join a flight force voiced by a veteran cast, featuring Japanese talent from Sailor Moon, Neon Genesis Evangelion, Gundam, Naruto & One Piece.
